+import { join } from 'path';
+
+/** @type {import('tailwindcss').Config}*/
+const config = {
+	content: [
+		'./src/**/*.{html,js,svelte,ts}',
+		// 3. Append the path to the Skeleton package
+		join(require.resolve(
+			'@skeletonlabs/skeleton'),
+			'../**/*.{html,js,svelte,ts}'
+		)
+	],
+	theme: {
+		extend: {}
+	},
+
+	plugins: [
+		skeleton
+	]
+};
+
+module.exports = config;
